book.title: The Cleric Quintet: The Chaos Curse (The Cleric Quintet #5)
book.description: Storyline: The prequel series to The Ghost King comes to an explosive end! Cadderly journeys home to the Edificant Library, hoping to rebuild his shattered life - but the chaos curse has one last surprise in store for him. Failure means the loss of his beloved Danica, success might usher in a new era for the followers of Denier.\n
book.author: R.A. Salvatore
